comments: Tate (HOU) establishes himself in a screening position in Nunn's (MIA) path and gives him a step to avoid contact.
Butler (MIA) makes contact to Tate's (HOU) arm and contact affects his driving shot attempt.
Tate (HOU) initiates contact to Adebayo's (MIA) lower body and contact affects his SQBR.
Adebayo (MIA) clamps House Jr.'s (HOU) arm and the contact affects his ability to defend. Replay review of the foul called on Adebayo (MIA) pursuant to a coach?s challenge was deemed unsuccessful.
Butler (MIA) makes incidental contact to Wall's (HOU) hand after the release of jump shot attempt.
Wall (HOU) briefly places his hand to Butler's (MIA) shoulder and quickly removes it before the start of his upward shooting motion.
Brown (HOU) and Iguodala (MIA) engage and disengage with one another during rebounding.
Tate (HOU) commits a take foul on Butler (MIA).
Nunn (MIA) makes clean contact with the ball before incidental contact occurs with Wall (HOU).
Wall (HOU) commits a take foul on Strus (MIA).
